Definition: a type of LCD display used for some portable computers
Example: parallel wires run both vertically and horizontally and pixels are turned on when the wires intersecting at that pixel are both energized; passive matrix displays are generally inferior to active matrix displays
Synonyms: liquid_crystal_display, a, type, of, LCD, display, used, for, some, portable, computers, parallel, wires, run, both, vertically, and, horizontally, pixels, are, turned, on, when, the, intersecting, at, that, pixel, energized, passive, matrix, displays, generally, inferior, to, active
Category: noun.artifact
